| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0054 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0c45aad2-291d-5b06-ac69-30617d0cc2f5"
